{"id":"8534","user":{"id":"101860","nickname":"四片叶de三叶吖","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FqcR23gyTBxqpGDVypZpJe8hw4uq","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【少院士讲堂】第七课—BOX2.0牌坊的建造","content":"<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fk9oVd-oOy-M7HFh-IkMUFdKkV6h\"><br></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">呦呦呦~又是我</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/emoji/codemao/2.gif\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 今天我们来讲牌坊的建造，</font></p>\n<p><span><br></span></p>\n<p><span>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; </span><span><font size=\"6\" color=\"#ff0000\">&nbsp;</font><font size=\"5\"><font color=\"#ff0000\">pái&nbsp;</font> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <font color=\"#00ffff\">&nbsp; &nbsp;fang</font></font></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font color=\"#00ff00\"> &nbsp;</font><font size=\"7\"><font color=\"#00ff00\">牌&nbsp; &nbsp; </font><font color=\"#ffcc00\">坊</font></font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; <font size=\"4\">在中国传统建筑中，牌坊可是有很大的地位，</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 那么什么是牌坊呢？大家来了解它吧！</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; </font><font size=\"5\">一.相关资料</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 牌坊，中华特色建筑文化之一。是封建社会为表彰功勋、科第、德政以及忠孝节义所立的建筑物。也有一些宫观寺庙以牌坊作为山门的，还有的是用来标明地名的。又名牌楼.</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;<img><img></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;</font><font size=\"5\"> 二.种类&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 1.柱出头式</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 顾名思义，这类牌楼的间柱是高出明楼楼顶的</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 2.不出头式</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 这类牌楼的最高峰是明楼的正脊</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 宫苑之内的牌楼，则大都是不出头式，而街道上的牌楼则大都是冲天式。</font></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; 当然啦~说这些建造才是最重要的嘛，以下为正文建造</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<font size=\"5\">建筑教程</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp;&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 第一关：萌新极简牌坊</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 难度：*</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 细节修饰：*</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 大小：*</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 赵铁柱盖新（坊）</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 两根柱立起来&nbsp;</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FnNCEtwUvrl2JqdsEcsaits5VTyx\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 主梁 666</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fo1SuU205H4HhwYOphcVlXOvRYv5\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 太小了，稍作微调</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/Fv1QHgh2K6Tahh529H_GWeHEwPHD\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">再搭一根梁</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FrD9QpEyQEhsVezpPPJc7Nl-IwiI\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">这可能是最简单的了，适于小型建筑，不用盖瓦QWQ</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><br></font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 第二关：新手进阶牌坊</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 较正常的牌坊</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 难度： **</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 细节修饰：**</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 大小：*</font></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 每日立两根柱，注意两柱的间隔，单数！<font>&nbsp;&nbsp;</font><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FguPL1Q1_RKmoruDIA71scVuNyA3\"></font></p>\n<p><span><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 再来两根，单数</font></span></p>\n<p><font size=\"4\"><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FgTtjVnlIj0XcS-AMGh9F-bVa4LO\"><span><br></span></font></p>\n<p><span><font size=\"4\">&nbsp; 基本形起来&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;</font></span